{"tid":1460774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[記者會精華]鄧炳強同警方高層出賣前線警員","createTime":"2019-08-13T04:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:56:12.000Z","uid":273207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3d7d80a3ba9e693b0b350da66fbe23073b06169","tid":1460774,"uid":273207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"聽左成個記者會，除去一大堆廢話之外，最精彩就係言談之間鄧炳強一直將責任卸比前線警員。<br />\n「根據守則，我地係會使用最底武力，但最後決定都係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線警員</span>根據當時情況決定</span></strong>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「我地既指示係唔會叫假扮示威者既人進行非法行為」(內心OS: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但佢地自己亂黎就唔關我地班高層事架</span></strong></span>)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，鄧炳強同警方高層想表達既係「我地高層發出既指示好清晰，跟足守則，至於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中低層班嗰班點執行就唔關我地事</span></span></strong>。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(而真相係點，就真係得喺佢地下面直接收指示既中高層先知)<br />\n<br />\n若果之後真係會成立獨立調查委員，警方班高層都只會拎中層或者<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線警員出黎祭旗</span></strong></span>。警方高層繼續喺冷氣房跳職場卸膊操。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當警察笑緊班示威者係甲由既時候，其實<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線警員</span>已經成為左鄧炳強同警方高層，腳下既<span style=\"color: red;\">甲由屍體</span></span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab331244e695b06c85408d2f3681e4b360b29eb4","tid":1460774,"uid":266617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:56:01.000Z","msg":"比現任一哥更識得使用安全套<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a5a327b0adb71a4d8ce6fc29a1da22e6cbacec","tid":1460774,"uid":273207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"}]}